ac73 toc-number\">6</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Park Type Guide</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">7</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Map &amp; Neighborhoods</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">8</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Planning Essentials</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">9</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Expert Advice</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">10</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Full Directory</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">11</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Owner &amp; Franchise</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Alexandria</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">Premier Dog City</p><h1>Dog Parks in Alexandria, VA</h1><p class=\"hero-description\">Experience the historic charm and modern pet amenities of Alexandria, where dog-friendly waterfront walks and scenic off-leash retreats define the city&#x27;s vibrant canine culture.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Alexandria, VA, is a masterclass in urban pet friendliness, recently ranked as the #2 best city for dogs in the United States. With an estimated 80,000 pets sharing the city with 160,000 residents, the infrastructure is built around canine inclusion. The region is anchored by the scenic <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.alexandriava.gov/DogParks\">Founders Park</a> along the Potomac, offering a community-driven off-leash retreat near Old Town. For those seeking structured play, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.alexandriava.gov/DogParks\">Simpson Stadium Dog Park</a> provides a well-lit, fenced environment with dedicated space for families. Our <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/states/virginia\">Virginia state directory</a> verifies these social hubs, showcasing a commitment to pet wellness that earned the city a &#x27;Better City for Pets&#x27; certification.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Beyond the sprawling acreage of <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.alexandriava.gov/DogParks\">Duke Street Dog Park</a> and the waterfront views of Windmill Hill, Alexandria enforces strict safety standards to ensure a harmonious environment. Owners must navigate a 24/7 leash law on all public grounds outside of designated exercise areas, with local enforcement prioritizing responsible handling and valid licensing. This balance of freedom and regulation allows the city&#x27;s vibrant dog-friendly culture to thrive, from the wood-chipped runs of <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.alexandriava.gov/DogParks\">Dog Run Park at Carlyle</a> to the shaded creek-side trails of Ben Brenman. Whether utilizing our <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/owner-resources\">owner resources</a> or participating in annual pet parades, Alexandria provides a world-class &#x27;third place&#x27; for pets and their people.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->18+ local exercise areas</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Top-ranked pet safety</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Alexandria dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/alexandria/hero.webp\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Alexandria</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Alexandria<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Verified ratings, review volume, and park availability updated directly from our community directory.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">National Ranking</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">#2 Best Dog City</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Ranked second nationally for its ratio of pet services, boarding facilities, and accessible park acreage.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Social Pillars</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Nighttime Play</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Facilities like Simpson Stadium remain lit until 10 PM, supporting the schedules of active urban commuters.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Coastal Recreation</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Waterfront Access</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Founders Park and Windmill Hill offer unique off-leash zones with panoramic views of the Potomac River.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-header\"><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">Most common amenities</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">What people are looking for and finding in <!-- -->Alexandria<!-- -->.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4d