">Local Districts</span><h2>Where to play in <!-- -->Alexandria</h2><p>Semantic clusters of dog-friendly highlights broken down by neighborhood.</p></div><div class=\"collection-grid\" style=\"margin-top:40px\"><article class=\"collection-card\" style=\"border:1px solid #f1f5f9;background:#f8fafc\"><div class=\"collection-card-head\"><span class=\"collection-pill\">0<!-- --> spots found</span><h3>Old Town</h3></div><p>Historic heart with waterfront runs like Founders Park.</p><div class=\"collection-card-footer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta text-link\">Browse directory<i class=\"bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></button></div></article><article class=\"collection-card\" style=\"border:1px solid #f1f5f9;background:#f8fafc\"><div class=\"collection-card-head\"><span class=\"collection-pill\">0<!-- --> spots found</span><h3>Del Ray</h3></div><p>Artsy, eclectic hub known for its intense pet-friendly culture.</p><div class=\"collection-card-footer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta text-link\">Browse directory<i class=\"bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></button></div></article><article class=\"collection-card\" style=\"border:1px solid #f1f5f9;background:#f8fafc\"><div class=\"collection-card-head\"><span class=\"collection-pill\">0<!-- --> spots found</span><h3>Carlyle</h3></div><p>Modern district featuring centrally located 24/7 dog runs.</p><div class=\"collection-card-footer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta text-link\">Browse directory<i class=\"bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></button></div></article></div></div></div></section><section id=\"map-and-neighborhoods\" class=\"map-experience-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO